## Philosophy
Big Tech is fundamentally distorting the tech landscape and we need to divest from centralized platforms instead of just starting over with each new one that comes along. This isn't anything revolutionary - the Fediverse movement closely aligns so the goal of this list is to keep a running list of tech that has good fundamentals so people can make better choices!

### Communication / Messaging
Signal - open source, free 
Proton - open source, free - with paid tiers

### Dating Apps
Alovoa - open source

### Social Media

Buffer - they aren't open source but their salary transparency approach and anti-growth model is something we should all support

